Message:
Big Sis? Where are you?!
Please, say something!

Ohh... Th-That thing’s...
been burnt by lightning...

There’s only one dead
body here, and it’s been
struck by lightning...

There’s no way...
That can’t be her!

S-See, there’s no way that
these pieces of coal are...!

It looks just like my
good luck charm...
